  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "VENTURE PRESS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "305 STUDIO BUILDING",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "1718 SHERMAN AVENUE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "EVANSTON, ILLINOIS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Augst 5, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Boise, Idaho",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Dear Mr. [REDACTED] b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "It seems that Mr. [REDACTED] of the Chicago Times got the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "story from Mr. [REDACTED], because he called me, told me he was",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "running it. I knew only what you'd told me over the phone.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Now, it seems the newspapers are pestering the very devil out",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "of all you fellows. [REDACTED] wired me for instructions, and I b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "told him to say nothing to the newspapers, because he'll look",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "silly if the army explains this as \"meteors\" or something like",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "that.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "I don't blame you for being alarmed, but I trust you've had no",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "trouble in your flying since then. Let's get that straight--",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "there's no horrible plot involved. It's probably true that the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "two men killed were just accidents. It could be true that it",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "was not an accident, but I don't think there was any connection",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "with the disks, or anything of that nature, nor is the material",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "from Murray Island to blame.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Certainly I don't think you'd suffer from completing your report",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "on your mission, and sending me your affidavit. Also, you'll",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "have some money coming for that, and no sense to tossing that out",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "of the window. It is unfortunate that the thing seemed so big",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "you had to call in army intelligence, but it will take them a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "long time to proceed to the point I've reached in this disk mystery.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "You see, you aren't the first to see them. They've been known",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "for nearly forty years, and I have ample proof of that. But",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "your experience was the first real break toward a solution. I'd",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "hate to have you drop the matter when all remaining to do is to",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "file your report with me.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "b7c [REDACTED] is willing to contribute his share. I hope you will too.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "This thing must not be hushed up and forgotten. It's much too",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "important to the people of America, if not the world. And no",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "censorship of the matter is legal. You needn't fear that angle.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "You certainly did a bang-up job of investigation, also you wrote",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "one of the best articles about your June 24 experience I've ever",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "seen. Please do the same on this last business. You owe it to",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "those two men who were killed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "I'd also like to know what developed on those pictures you took",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "of those \"ducks\", or whatever they were.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    }
  ],
  "blockCount": null
}
